      <div>
        <p class="section-eyebrow">The Beginning</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-6">July 2016: The First Circle</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          It started with a simple question: "What if we could experience music without the pressure of performance?"
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Atray and a few friends gathered in a living room in Jaipur. No agenda, no setlist, no expectations. Just people, instruments, and the willingness to be vulnerable together.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          That night, something unexpected happened. We didn't just make music - we made connection. And Kythera was born.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="text-gray-400">Photo: First Kythera gathering</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

